  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK753">
<l>poruḷeṉṉum poyyā viḷakka miruḷaṟukku</l>
<l>meṇṇiya tēyattuc ceṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The imperishable light of wealth goes into regions desired (by its owner) and destroys the darkness (of enmity therein).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
